<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Truckle-bed" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Truckle-bed,</orth> a bed that runs on wheels and may be pushed under another: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.1.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 1, 39</bibl>. cf. <emph>Standing-bed.</emph>
